05:43.663 --> 05:46.309
That was so great how
you worked together.

05:46.344 --> 05:48.670
Why don't you do that all the time?

05:52.699 --> 05:57.548
<i>I can't feel my legs anymore!</i>

05:57.615 --> 06:02.553
- Hey, look at that! It's a tiny temple!
- It's just where Garnet

06:02.620 --> 06:05.422
said it would be.
The heaven beetle should be inside.

06:05.490 --> 06:09.159
Check it out!
It's even got a little beetle

06:09.260 --> 06:13.656
<i>bedroom and little beetle bongos
and a little beetle baby book.</i>

06:13.691 --> 06:17.512
But where's the beetle?
It's supposed to be here.

06:17.547 --> 06:22.383
The heaven beetle wouldn't leave, would it?
Oh, it could be anywhere!

06:22.418 --> 06:24.693
Uh, maybe you
should freak out some more.

06:24.793 --> 06:28.412
- That's really gonna help us find it.
- I can't believe your attitude, Amethyst.

06:28.479 --> 06:31.548
And now you're just slouching
over here doing nothing!

06:31.607 --> 06:35.352
Hey! It's not my fault the beetle
isn't there! Why do you have

06:35.420 --> 06:38.294
<i>- to make things worse by squawking at me?
- I don't squawk!</i>

06:38.356 --> 06:41.525
<i>Yeah, you're squawking and
commenting on my posture!</i>

06:41.593 --> 06:46.230
Hey! Cut it out!
You're scaring Steven Jr.!

06:50.904 --> 06:52.358
My son.

06:59.191 --> 07:04.480
- In here, guys!
- It swallowed my spear!

07:04.515 --> 07:09.486
Guys, this is great! Now's the
perfect time for you two to form Opal!

07:23.278 --> 07:26.092
<i>Oh, brother.</i>

07:35.623 --> 07:39.683
Ugh! So, you wanna try that
again with less hitting

07:39.751 --> 07:43.587
- me in the face this time?
- Well, it would have worked if your

07:43.688 --> 07:47.524
- movements weren't so erratic and formless.
- So, it was all my fault?

07:47.592 --> 07:51.328
You totally weren't
even trying to sync with my dancing.

07:51.396 --> 07:56.581
- You should know how I dance by now!
- Stop! Come on, guys!

07:56.616 --> 07:59.775
Please stop fighting!
If you can't get along with each other,

07:59.810 --> 08:04.107
I might never get to see
your awesome fusion power!

08:04.175 --> 08:08.521
And I might get
eaten by a giant bird!

08:12.081 --> 08:14.385
- Steven!
- Unh!

08:17.522 --> 08:21.591
Steven Jr.!
How can you eat at a time like this?

08:21.659 --> 08:26.163
Hey, is that the heaven beetle?
Let me see it!

08:26.230 --> 08:32.993
Hey! Be a good goat
and give me the magic bug!

08:36.034 --> 08:39.606
I got it!
No! B-bad goat!

08:39.640 --> 08:42.250
You're no son of mine!

08:45.911 --> 08:49.720
What's going on?!
Steven Jr.! Oooh!

09:00.140 --> 09:01.993
Opal?

09:12.276 --> 09:15.345
Hup!

09:16.445 --> 09:19.162
Stay low.

09:51.349 --> 09:57.737
Uh... do you...
know who I am?

09:58.456 --> 10:02.559
♪ all you wanna do is see me turn into ♪

10:02.627 --> 10:05.956
A giant woman.

10:08.650 --> 10:10.085
We're back!

10:10.120 --> 10:13.666
- The heaven beetle.
- I don't have it.

10:16.057 --> 10:19.701
- Unh!
- Amethyst, you got distracted!

10:19.736 --> 10:22.036
Hey! You were
the one getting carried away

10:22.071 --> 10:25.003
- with all those fancy backflips!
- Wait a sec.

10:25.038 --> 10:28.189
I've got the beetle!

10:28.867 --> 10:31.003
Good job, Steven.

10:33.613 --> 10:37.038
I also see you helped
your teammates fuse.

10:38.309 --> 10:41.116
And all I had to
do was get eaten by a bird.

10:41.151 --> 10:44.763
Nice work.
You'll be great at fusing one day.

10:45.072 --> 10:48.648
Yeah.
Wait. I can do that, too?!

